@startuml
title Deployment Diagram - Triển khai production dự kiến theo source hiện tại

skinparam componentStyle rectangle

package "Client Layer" {
node "Máy người dùng" as Client {
  artifact "Client Browser" as Browser
}
}

package "Application Layer" {
node "Web Server ASP.NET MVC" as WebServer {
  node "IIS hoặc Kestrel" as Host {
    artifact "ASP.NET MVC\nQuanLyDuAn.dll" as MvcApp
    component "Razor MVC\nControllers + Views" as MvcRuntime
    component "Cookie Authentication\nIdentity / Claims" as Auth
    component "Service Layer\nBusiness + Permission + Workflow" as BusinessServices
    component "Entity Framework Core\nQuanLyDuAnDbContext" as EFCore
    artifact "appsettings.json\nConnectionStrings.DefaultConnection\nAiApi.BaseUrl" as Config
    artifact "wwwroot\nstatic files, uploads" as StaticFiles
  }
}
}

package "AI Layer" {
node "FastAPI AI Server" as AiServer {
  artifact "FastAPI service\nuvicorn app.main:app" as FastApi
  component "REST API\n/health, /dataset/validate,\n/model/train, /analyze/delay-reason,\n/admin/model/*" as RestApi
  component "Python AI runtime\npandas, scikit-learn, joblib" as PythonAi
  artifact "Joblib Model\nreason_active.joblib" as JoblibModel
  artifact "Model Metadata\n*.metadata.json" as ModelMetadata
}
}

package "Database Layer" {
database "SQL Server" as SqlServer {
  artifact "QuanLyDuAnAI database" as Db
  artifact "Business schema\nDU_AN, CONG_VIEC, CT_CONG_VIEC,\nTIEN_DO_CONG_VIEC, DE_XUAT_*, NGAN_SACH" as BusinessSchema
  artifact "Identity schema\nAspNetUsers, AspNetRoles,\nAspNetRoleClaims, AspNetUserClaims" as IdentitySchema
  artifact "AI persisted data\nAI_DATASET, AI_KET_QUA,\nAI_NGUYEN_NHAN, AI_MODEL" as AiSchema
}
}

Browser --> Host : HTTPS
Host --> MvcApp : reverse proxy / process hosting
MvcApp --> MvcRuntime : xử lý request MVC
MvcRuntime --> Auth : cookie auth + identity claims
MvcRuntime --> BusinessServices : gọi service
BusinessServices --> EFCore : đọc/ghi DbContext
EFCore --> SqlServer : SQL Server protocol\nEntity Framework Core
MvcApp --> StaticFiles : phục vụ static/upload file

BusinessServices --> RestApi : REST API HTTP/HTTPS\nMVC là system-of-record
RestApi --> FastApi : nhận request
FastApi --> PythonAi : validate/train/analyze reason-only
PythonAi --> JoblibModel : load/save model
PythonAi --> ModelMetadata : đọc/ghi metadata

AiServer -[#red,dashed]-> SqlServer : không triển khai kết nối trực tiếp\nFastAPI chỉ compute AI
@enduml
